{"id": "art-113", "label": "Art. 113", "title": "Art. 113", "slug": "art-113", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 113 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>Adunarea\ngeneral&#259; extraordinar&#259; se <span class=SpellE>întrune&#351;te</span>\nori de câte ori este necesar a se lua o hot&#259;râre pentru:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)schimbarea\nformei juridice a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)mutarea\nsediului <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)schimbarea\nobiectului de activitate al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)<span\nclass=SpellE>înfiin&#355;area</span> sau <span class=SpellE>desfiin&#355;area</span>\nunor sedii secundare: sucursale, <span class=SpellE>agen&#355;ii</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;e</span> sau alte asemenea <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nf&#259;r&#259; personalitate juridic&#259;, dac&#259; prin actul constitutiv nu\nse prevede altfel;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)prelungirea\nduratei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)majorarea\ncapitalului social;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>g)reducerea\ncapitalului social sau reîntregirea lui prin emisiune de noi <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1122444624\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2336\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1122444624\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)fuziunea cu alte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nsau divizarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, inclusiv fuziunea\ntransfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> divizarea\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1238664096\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2335\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1238664096\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h<sup>1</sup>)transformarea transfrontalier&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>i)dizolvarea\nanticipat&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_685078166\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2334\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_685078166\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i<sup>1</sup>)[textul din Art. 113, litera I^1. din titlul\nIII, capitolul IV, <span class=SpellE>sectiunea</span> II a fost abrogat la\n21-iul-2019 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. 54, punctul 10. din\ncapitolul XI din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> 129/2019</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>j)conversia\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> dintr-o categorie în cealalt&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>k)conversia\nunei categorii de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span> în alt&#259;\ncategorie sau în <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>l)emisiunea\nde <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>m)oricare\nalt&#259; modificare a actului constitutiv sau oricare alt&#259; hot&#259;râre\npentru care este cerut&#259; aprobarea adun&#259;rii generale extraordinare.</span></p>"}